```py
InsertionSort(array: A):
    Integer: N = length(A)
    Integer: i = 1
  ❶ WHILE i < N:
        Type: current = A[i]
        Integer: j = i - 1  
      ❷ WHILE j >= 0 AND A[j] > current:
            A[j + 1] = A[j]
            j = j - 1
        A[j + 1] = current
        i = i + 1
```

```py
StringEqual(String: str1, String: str2):
    IF length(str1) != length(str2):
        return False
    Integer: N = length(str1)
    Integer: i = 0
    WHILE i < N AND str1[i] == str2[i]:
        i = i + 1
    return i == N
```
